
Privacy Policy - Job Huntr

Effective date: 08/2/2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to Job Huntr ("us", "we", or "our"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application Job Huntr (the "App").

By accessing or using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the practices described in this policy, please do not use the App.

2. Information We Collect

(a) Personal Information: When you use Job Huntr, we may collect certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you ("Personal Information"). This may include but is not limited to your name, email address, phone number, and location data.

(b) Non-Personal Information: We may also collect non-personal information about your device, usage patterns, and other technical information to improve the App's functionality and performance.

3. How We Use Your Information

(a) We may use your Personal Information for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain Job Huntr's functionality.
To personalize and improve user experience.
To respond to your requests, comments, or inquiries.
To send you promotional materials and updates about Job Huntr.
To enforce our Terms of Service and other legal agreements.
(b) We may use non-personal information for statistical analysis, troubleshooting, and enhancing the App's features.

4. Disclosure of Your Information

(a) We may share your Personal Information with third parties under the following circumstances:

With your consent.
To comply with legal obligations or enforce our rights.
To service providers who assist us in operating Job Huntr.
In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets.
(b) Non-personal information may be shared for various purposes, including marketing and analytics.

5. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your Personal Information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

6. Children's Privacy

Job Huntr is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective upon posting the revised policy on Job Huntr. Your continued use of the App after any changes will signify your acceptance of the modified Privacy Policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at hernandezchristian94@gmail.com.